# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  OpenBell — Environment Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and edit as needed.
# start.sh sources .env automatically.
# Lines starting with # are comments.

# ── Server ──
# OPENBELL_PORT=5000                        # Rust server listen port
# OPENBELL_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:5000  # Base URL for CV server + voice assistant
# OPENBELL_WS_URL=ws://localhost:5000/ws    # WebSocket URL for Tauri dashboard

# ── Physical doorbell relay ──
# Set this to enable ringing your house's existing wired chime.
# Examples:
#   Shelly 1:  http://<RELAY_IP>/relay/0?turn=on&timer=1
#   Tasmota:   http://<RELAY_IP>/cm?cmnd=Power%20On
# DOORBELL_RELAY_URL=

# ── Inter-process UDP (only change if running components on separate hosts) ──
# OPENBELL_RUST_HOST=127.0.0.1              # Rust server address for UDP audio
# OPENBELL_ASSISTANT_LISTEN_PORT=5004       # UDP: Rust → voice assistant
# OPENBELL_ASSISTANT_SEND_PORT=5005         # UDP: voice assistant → Rust
# OPENBELL_ASSISTANT_LISTEN=127.0.0.1:5004  # Full address Rust forwards mic audio to

# ── CV Server (YOLOv8) ──
# OPENBELL_YOLO_MODEL=yolov8s.pt            # Path to YOLO model weights
# OPENBELL_DEVICE=cuda                      # Inference device: cpu, cuda, cuda:0
# OPENBELL_PERSON_CONF=0.55                 # Minimum person detection confidence
# OPENBELL_INFERENCE_INTERVAL=0.5           # Seconds between inference frames
# OPENBELL_MIN_DETECTIONS=4                 # Consecutive detections to trigger event
# OPENBELL_PERSON_LEFT_TIMEOUT=5.0          # Seconds without detection → person_left

# ── Voice Assistant (Whisper + Piper) ──
# OPENBELL_WHISPER_MODEL=base               # Whisper model: tiny, base, small, medium
# OPENBELL_WHISPER_DEVICE=cpu               # Whisper device: cpu, cuda
# OPENBELL_WHISPER_COMPUTE=int8             # Whisper compute type
# OPENBELL_PIPER_VOICE=en_GB-jenny_dioco-medium  # Piper TTS voice
# OPENBELL_AUTO_ANSWER_SECS=5              # Auto-answer delay
# OPENBELL_LISTEN_TIMEOUT=8.0              # Max silence before ending listen
# OPENBELL_SILENCE_THRESHOLD=0.02          # Audio level below = silence
# OPENBELL_MAX_TURNS=3                     # Max conversation turns
# OPENBELL_MAX_SESSION=90.0                # Max session duration (seconds)

# ── Android app (build-time only) ──
# Set before running ./gradlew assembleDebug:
# OPENBELL_SERVER_URL=http://<YOUR_PC_IP>:5000
